## Obsidian Brain Structure

Vault lives at: `{{BRAIN_PATH}}/`

Flat structure — all content files live at the vault root. Only high-volume feeds and system folders get subdirectories.

```
Brain/
├── .obsidian/              <- Obsidian config (do not touch)
├── Templates/              <- Obsidian templates
├── Indexes/                <- Auto-maintained entity catalogs
├── Dashboard.md            <- Master index
├── Activity Log.md         <- Auto-maintained by brain-guard.sh
└── [Type] Entity - Desc.md <- All content files flat at root
```

